			<div class="col-sm-8 col-md-7 product-content">
				<div class="intro-text" itemprop="description">
					<p>Van Iperen Monoammonium Phosphate (MAP) Horticultural Grade is a very pure Phosphate fertilizer that dissolves rapidly and completely. Our product has a limited caking tendency and is recommended during root and shoot development in the early stages, through to flowering and early fruit set. The high level of Phosphate in our formula increases cell division and development of new plant tissue. The presence of Nitrogen contributes to early plant establishment and vegetative growth.</p>

				</div>
									<ul class="product-highlights">
													<li>Improves root and shoot growth</li>
													<li>Developed for fertigation in open field and greenhouses. Also suitable for foliar application</li>
											</ul>
				
				<div class="hidden-sm">
						<div class="product-application-icons">
		<h2 class="product-application-icons__title">Application</h2>
		<ul class="product-application-icons__icons">
									<li class="product-application-icons__icon">
